NT||
st||SK|e|MD|1sqjt987hj2dq95cak,s54hKQt43d87cQt85,sk3h5dAJ1064c97632,sA62hA9876dK32cJ4|SV|o|RH||AH|Board 2|MB|4SPPP|PC|hk|NT|^B@2
You are playing in the East position against South's contract of four spades. Partner opens the heart King.|
PG| ***** 24 ***** |


cp||AT| You see at once what you should do. You should overtake with your Ace,|
PG| ***** 25 ***** |


CP||PC|H5hAh2|
